title: Tarzan And The Trappers Gordon Scott

sources.title: Tarzan And The Trappers Gordon Scott
sources.description: Classic Action Film: Tarzan and the Trappers - After dispatching a ruthless hunter who traps animals for gain, he has to contend with his brother who is out for revenge. Tarzan and the Trappers (1960) Director: Charles F. Haas, Sandy Howard, H. Bruce Humberstone(uncredited) Writers: Edgar Rice Burroughs(characters), Frederick Schlick, Robert Leach Stars: Gordon Scott, Eve Brent, Rickie Sorensen Genre: Action, Adventure Country: United States Language: English Release Date: 21 March 1960 (Iran) Duration: 70 min Filming Location: Iverson Ranch - 1 Iverson Lane, Chatsworth, Los Angeles, California, USA Storyline: Tarzan deals with the villainous Schroeder, who is illegally collecting animals for zoos, only to be menaced by Schroeder's hunter brother Sikes, out for revenge, who teams up with greedy trader Lapin in a hunt for human game...Tarzan himself.
